https://www.stereolabs.com/developers/release
https://www.stereolabs.com/docs/installation/linux

INSTALL
cd -nereye indirdiysen-
sudo apt install zstd
chmod +x ZED_SDK_Ubuntu22_cuda12.1_v4.1.0.zstd.run
./ZED_SDK_Ubuntu22_cuda12.1_v4.1.0.zstd.run

To install the ZED SDK without checking that CUDA is installed, add the skip_cuda option.
./ZED_SDK_Ubuntu22_cuda12.1_v4.1.0.zstd.run -- silent skip_cuda
